{"tid":964414,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[原來是0] F4 言承旭 驚爆hehe情,與男星酒店纏綿5日","createTime":"2019-01-01T09:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T13:02:53.000Z","uid":53060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1be08d63c500ab69b54546edfc902956e9870fa2","tid":964414,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:56:30.000Z","msg":"記者楊凱婷／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n41歲F4男神言承旭與名模林志玲情傳多年，兩人的感情動向一直備受外界矚目，豈料今（30）日言承旭卻在大陸遭偷拍，疑似和某男星互動親暱，在酒店同居5日，陷入同志疑雲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZylN5yYu54CdHDMpoq7.YQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/setn_com_683/427f1387cb107e6ec465a11aad5c0137\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZylN5yYu54CdHDMpoq7.YQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn_com_683%2F427f1387cb107e6ec465a11aad5c0137&h=7671ea15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼▲言承旭、田家達被拍到在酒店同居5日。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/G_FeJ0l7PDDZqWLhderwAA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDMyO2g9MzA4/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/setn_com_683/5afae4fe37b448934ee00b2571c7a048\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FG_FeJ0l7PDDZqWLhderwAA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDMyO2g9MzA4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn_com_683%2F5afae4fe37b448934ee00b2571c7a048&h=f487b229&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據陸媒《百度》報導，有大陸網友目擊言承旭和小1歲的藝人田家達一起在酒店同居5日，兩人為避嫌不想被人發現，期間都沒有一起出門，即便是叫外賣來吃，都是一次買一份，分開購買，且田家達過去曾被冠上男星陳德烈「男友」的頭銜，其性向一直都是個謎團。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CmGlrwUr1256LlznUdOTkg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDQwO2g9MjQ1/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/setn_com_683/77fd91d315a767b77314e1a877f38e8c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCmGlrwUr1256LlznUdOTkg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDQwO2g9MjQ1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn_com_683%2F77fd91d315a767b77314e1a877f38e8c&h=32bd5b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼▲言承旭、田家達疑似在酒店同居5日。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/symi7IROmUg640UKMtLuag--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDQwO2g9Mjg2/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/setn_com_683/33fccb28a6e2388a908eb2ca64b4105c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fsymi7IROmUg640UKMtLuag--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDQwO2g9Mjg2%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn_com_683%2F33fccb28a6e2388a908eb2ca64b4105c&h=c23fab33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少網友看了出櫃傳聞，都不敢相信表示，「我不相信阿旭是這樣的人啊！」、「兩個男生朋友一起出去玩很奇怪嗎？」日前林志玲無預警PO出男女剪影的交纏接吻照，讓許多網友都以為是她和言承旭舊情復燃，不過事後志玲姐姐也潑了大家冷水坦言「只是廣告。」"},{"pid":"d4bb884ae91de6268e4134f0a70e992dc8c25600","tid":964414,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CMmmncbnKdClP4TiigcWsw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjU2O2g9ODgw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2018-12/5d9799d0-0cae-11e9-bb8f-a2beaecd160c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCMmmncbnKdClP4TiigcWsw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjU2O2g9ODgw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2018-12%2F5d9799d0-0cae-11e9-bb8f-a2beaecd160c&h=55a07109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n言承旭撇志玲同居田家達"},{"pid":"3e530fa50749dcfdebd8575dfc37b1cfeba10841","tid":964414,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IP3XtgHDMVU/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%